Package: ClustR
Type: Package
Title: Deep and Classical Variable Clustering Toolbox
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Riad", "Sahrane", , "m.riadsahrane@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Tools for clustering variables using classical and deep-learning approaches.
    Includes a deep autoencoder-based clustering engine (ClustDeepVar),
    PC1-based clustering, visualisation helpers, and a Shiny dashboard.
    Deep models rely on 'keras3' with the TensorFlow backend.
